---
title: Thai-Spiced Chicken & Broccoli with Ginger-Coconut Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: This fragrant meal packs flavour in every bite. From the ginger-coconut rice to the spiced chicken brimming with sweet and savoury notes and the colourful veggies, this is so much better than takeaway.
